"""
BankVoiceAI — Fetch.ai Native Payment Gateway (PRODUCTION v3)
=============================================================
WHAT'S NEW vs your existing gateway:
  1. Full uAgents Payment Protocol (seller role):
       RequestPayment → CommitPayment → CompletePayment / CancelPayment
     — exactly as described in Fetch.ai Innovation Lab Doc 2
  2. PostgreSQL persistence (subscriptions survive server restarts)
  3. Renewal engine — checks expiry daily, auto-sends new RequestPayment
  4. Tier-access gating — every agent call checks DB, not memory
  5. FAILED path properly wired to CancelPayment (was missing)

Plans (FET / month):
  PILOT      →   0 FET  → 30-day free trial
  STARTER    → 250 FET  → customer_service, fraud_detection, onboarding
  GROWTH     → 750 FET  → + collections, sales, compliance
  ENTERPRISE → 2000 FET → all agents + unlimited calls

Fetch.ai Innovation Lab Doc 2 reference:
  verify_fet_payment_to_agent() → maps to FetchLedgerVerifier.verify_payment()
  CommitPayment handler         → maps to handle_commit_payment()
  CompletePayment               → sent on success
  CancelPayment                 → sent on failure (was missing before)
"""

import asyncio
import hashlib
import hmac
import json
import logging
import os
